    <span>Thrive on Thrift</span>
  </a>
  <button class="nav-toggle" aria-label="Toggle menu" aria-expanded="false" onclick="
    const n=document.getElementById('primary-nav');
    const open=n.classList.toggle('open');
    this.setAttribute('aria-expanded', open);
  "><span></span></button>
  <nav id="primary-nav">
    <a href="#about">Our Story</a>
    <a href="#how">How Pickup Works</a>
    <a href="#accept">What We Accept</a>
    <a href="#visit">Visit Us</a>
    <a class="btn btn-primary" href="/donate">Schedule a Pickup</a>
  </nav>
</header>

<section class="hero">
  <div class="wrap">
    <span class="eyebrow">Sterlington, Louisiana · A project of Thrive Ministries</span>
    <svg class="wordmark" viewBox="0 0 760 240" role="img" aria-label="Thrive on Thrift">
      <path id="arc" d="M 40 190 Q 380 30 720 190" fill="none"/>
      <text font-size="72" font-weight="600" fill="var(--ink)">
        <textPath href="#arc" startOffset="50%" text-anchor="middle">Thrive on Thrift</textPath>
      </text>
    </svg>
    <p class="lede">A nonprofit thrift store where every donation funds job training and emergency help for families right here in Ouachita Parish.</p>
    <div class="ctas">
      <a class="btn btn-primary" href="/donate">Schedule a Free Pickup</a>
      <a class="btn btn-ghost" href="#visit">Visit the Store</a>
    </div>
    <p class="hero-hours">Pickups run 9:30am–5:00pm, Monday–Saturday · Drop-offs welcome anytime we're open</p>
  </div>

  <svg class="vine" viewBox="0 0 800 40" preserveAspectRatio="none" aria-hidden="true">
    <path d="M0 22 C 90 4, 170 40, 260 20 S 430 2, 520 22 S 690 38, 800 18"/>
    <circle cx="118" cy="14" r="3.4"/>
    <circle cx="300" cy="30" r="3.4"/>
    <circle cx="478" cy="10" r="3.4"/>
    <circle cx="650" cy="13" r="5.2"/>
  </svg>
</section>

<section class="section-deep" id="about">
  <div class="wrap about-grid">
    <div>
      <span class="eyebrow">Our story</span>
      <h2 class="section-title">Donated goods, given a second life — and a purpose.</h2>
      <p>Thrive on Thrift opened in 2017 as a project of Thrive Ministries, a Sterlington nonprofit that helps neighbors find steady work and supports women and families rebuilding after a crisis or a house fire. Every item on our shelves was donated by someone nearby, and every sale goes straight back into those programs.</p>
      <p>We call it a "boutiquey" thrift store on purpose — donations are sorted, cleaned, and priced with care, so shopping here feels less like digging through a bin and more like finding something good on purpose.</p>
    </div>
    <div class="stat-row">
      <div class="stat"><div class="num">2017</div><div class="label">Open since, as a Thrive Ministries program</div></div>
      <div class="stat"><div class="num">Mon–Sat</div><div class="label">In the shop, 9:00am – 5:00pm CT</div></div>
      <div class="stat"><div class="num">5</div><div class="label">Donation categories we pick up: clothing, furniture, toys, household, electronics</div></div>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>

<section id="how">
  <div class="wrap">
    <div class="section-head">
      <span class="eyebrow">From your porch to our shelves</span>
      <h2 class="section-title">How a pickup works</h2>
    </div>
    <div class="steps">
      <div class="step">
        <span class="n">01</span>
        <h3>Tell us what you have</h3>
        <p>Fill out the online form with your address, item categories, and a preferred date and time.</p>
        <span class="tag">Status: new</span>
      </div>
      <div class="step">
        <span class="n">02</span>
        <h3>We confirm a window</h3>
        <p>Our team checks the van's calendar and locks in a pickup time during store hours.</p>
        <span class="tag">Status: scheduled</span>
      </div>
      <div class="step">
        <span class="n">03</span>
        <h3>The van comes to you</h3>
        <p>A crew arrives at your driveway, porch, or garage — no need to haul anything yourself.</p>
        <span class="tag">Pickup day</span>
      </div>
      <div class="step">
        <span class="n">04</span>
        <h3>It goes back to the community</h3>
        <p>Your donation is sorted, priced, and shelved — and the proceeds fund Thrive Ministries' programs.</p>
        <span class="tag">Status: completed</span>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>

<section class="section-deep" id="accept">
  <div class="wrap">
    <div class="section-head">
      <span class="eyebrow">What we accept</span>
      <h2 class="section-title">Gently used, and still good</h2>
    </div>
    <div class="cats">
      <div class="cat-card">
        <svg viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="1.6" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round"><path d="M9 3 4.5 6 6.5 9 8 7.7V20h8V7.7L17.5 9l2-3L15 3c0 1.4-1.6 2.5-3 2.5S9 4.4 9 3Z"/></svg>
        <span>Clothing</span>
      </div>
      <div class="cat-card">
        <svg viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="1.6" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round"><path d="M5 11v6M19 11v9M5 11c0-2.2 1.8-4 4-4h6c2.2 0 4 1.8 4 4M5 14h14M9 17v3M15 17v3"/></svg>
        <span>Furniture</span>
      </div>
      <div class="cat-card">
        <svg viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="1.6" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round"><rect x="4.5" y="4.5" width="15" height="15" rx="3.5"/><circle cx="12" cy="12" r="2.6"/></svg>
        <span>Toys</span>
      </div>
      <div class="cat-card">
        <svg viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="1.6" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round"><path d="M4 11 12 4l8 7M6 10v10h12V10"/></svg>
        <span>Household</span>
      </div>
      <div class="cat-card">
        <svg viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="1.6" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round"><path d="M9 2v6M15 2v6M6 8h12v4c0 4-3 6-6 6s-6-2-6-6Zm6 10v4"/></svg>
        <span>Electronics</span>
      </div>
    </div>
    <p class="cats-note">Not sure if something qualifies? Mention it in the notes field when you schedule a pickup — our team will follow up before pickup day. Excellent or good condition is preferred.</p>
  </div>
</section>

<section id="visit">
  <div class="wrap visit-grid">
    <div class="visit-card">
      <h3>Visit the store</h3>
      <div class="visit-row">
        <svg viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="1.6" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round"><path d="M12 21s7-6.3 7-11a7 7 0 0 0-14 0c0 4.7 7 11 7 11Z"/><circle cx="12" cy="10" r="2.4"/></svg>
        <span>10010 US-165 (Hwy 165 N), Sterlington, LA 71280</span>
      </div>
      <div class="visit-row">
        <svg viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="1.6" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round"><path d="M4 5c0 8 7 15 15 15l2-4-5-2-2 2c-2-1-4-3-5-5l2-2-2-5Z"/></svg>
        <a href="tel:3186652288">(318) 665-2288</a>
      </div>
      <table class="hours">
        <tr><td>Mon – Sat</td><td>9:00am – 5:00pm</td></tr>
        <tr><td>Sunday</td><td>Closed</td></tr>
      </table>
      <div class="ctas">
        <a class="btn btn-primary" href="https://maps.google.com/?q=10010+US-165,+Sterlington,+LA+71280" target="_blank" rel="noopener">Get Directions</a>
        <a class="btn btn-ghost" href="/donate">Schedule a Pickup</a>
      </div>
      <p style="margin-top:18px;font-size:14.5px;color:#5b5740">Prefer to drop off yourself? Bring items by anytime we're open — no appointment needed.</p>
    </div>
    <div class="visit-illustration">
      <svg viewBox="0 0 320 260" fill="none" stroke="var(--olive-deep)" stroke-width="1.7" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" aria-hidden="true">
        <rect x="30" y="90" width="260" height="140" rx="4"/>
        <path d="M30 90 10 60h300l-20 30"/>
        <path d="M10 60 30 30h260l20 30"/>
        <line x1="40" y1="70" x2="50" y2="45"/>
        <line x1="90" y1="70" x2="100" y2="45"/>
        <line x1="140" y1="70" x2="150" y2="45"/>
        <line x1="190" y1="70" x2="200" y2="45"/>
        <line x1="240" y1="70" x2="250" y2="45"/>
        <rect x="60" y="140" width="60" height="90"/>
        <rect x="190" y="140" width="60" height="50"/>
        <line x1="190" y1="165" x2="250" y2="165"/>
        <circle cx="90" cy="200" r="3" fill="var(--gold)" stroke="none"/>
      </svg>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>

